{"tid":2298811,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"外交部：英國無資格當判官　促摒棄殖民主義思想","createTime":"2020-11-24T10:05:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T01:35:19.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":55,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"3a824d0c9572d008370068dd955592bc4131a531","tid":2298811,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T10:05:36.000Z","msg":"在北京，外交部回應英國政府的「香港半年報告」時敦促英方摒棄殖民主義思想，收起虛偽和雙重標準，停止干涉別國內政。<br />\n<br />\n發言人趙立堅說，香港是中國的特別行政區，英國對香港事務沒有任何監督權和所謂的道義責任，無權借《中英聯合聲明》干預香港事務，強調過去英國在殖民統治時期沒給過香港民主，今天，英國沒有資格當判官。<br />\n<br />\n英國政府早前向國會提交「香港半年報告」，指中國政府違反《中英聯合聲明》。外相藍韜文說，開始諮詢英國最高法院院長，何時要檢視英國法官，繼續擔任香港終審法院非常任法官是否合適。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561668-20201124.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561668-20201124.htm&d=axquv7MewSEsfpkSD3%2FEaHs01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=f6f4458e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561668-20201124.htm&h=7ed7f2bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561668-20201124.htm</a>"},{"pid":"0c4733b2ca35be6486d5445256bd5d1e6728da66","tid":2298811,"uid":76804,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T10:09:58.000Z","msg":"宜家係支那用緊殖民主義管香港喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dbd2c6f1ba812579afeeb87d12ff69b44e36918","tid":2298811,"uid":153811,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"3a824d0c9572d008370068dd955592bc4131a531","tid":2298811,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T10:05:36.000Z","msg":"在北京，外交部回應英國政府的「香港半年報告」時敦促英方摒棄殖民主義思想，收起虛偽和雙重標準，停止干涉別國內政。<br />\n<br />\n發言人趙立堅說，香港是中國的特別行政區，英國對香港事務沒有任何監督權和所謂的道義責任，無權借《中英聯合聲明》干預香港事務，強調過去英國在殖民統治時期沒給過香港民主，今天，英國沒有資格當判官。<br />\n<br />\n英國政府早前向國會提交「香港半年報告」，指中國政府違反《中英聯合聲明》。外相藍韜文說，開始諮詢英國最高法院院長，何時要檢視英國法官，繼續擔任香港終審法院非常任法官是否合適。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561668-20201124.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561668-20201124.htm&d=axquv7MewSEsfpkSD3%2FEaHs01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=f6f4458e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561668-20201124.htm&h=7ed7f2bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561668-20201124.htm</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T10:10:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eaf0f51db74debddc548dd01a7d182cc425a567","tid":2298811,"uid":44171,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T10:11:05.000Z","msg":"佢有份簽聯合聲明都無權，咁中國當初又點有權收返香港？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"391eac875a1aeb26e0ed7e6f516f39d9f4465136","tid":2298811,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T10:11:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f5a8884da4eaa5ef726fd9e7925793c9107b2f1","tid":2298811,"uid":79117,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T10:11:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5e88bcce3b9bb67e98de40d3fbcadf2c50072502","tid":2298811,"uid":290118,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T10:11:18.000Z","msg":"人哋同你係締約國，大家咁高咁大咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fcb828b27ba71a27eb80ad0d1fe5b50c86ef348","tid":2298811,"uid":185656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T10:11:55.000Z","msg":"支那停止干預香港內政未?"},{"pid":"b492e9b987e5c1e217fc732809c75a3138ffbde3","tid":2298811,"uid":284855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T10:12:32.000Z","msg":"咁介意做乜<img src=\"/asse